NetHack-de is an attempt at a German translation of "NetHack":http://www.nethack.org/.

The current state of the translation is work-in-progress.

At the moment around
{execute: cd ../src; ./statistik | tail -1 | tr -s \  | cut -f 5 -d \  | cut -f 1 -d .}%
of the in-game text is translated.
Detailed information about the progress of the translation can be found on the "status page":status.html.

The source code and binary packages for Windows and Linux are available from "Sourceforge":http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=191550.

